@Ingestion.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001
@CorrelationId = {{$guid}}

### Health - overall
GET {{Ingestion.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Health - liveness
GET {{Ingestion.Api_HostAddress}}/health/live
Accept: application/json

### Health - readiness
GET {{Ingestion.Api_HostAddress}}/health/ready
Accept: application/json

### Ingest single event
POST {{Ingestion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ingest/events
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{CorrelationId}}

{
  "eventType": "order.created",
  "source": "checkout-service",
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-03T14:30:00Z",
  "payload": {
    "orderId": "ord_123",
    "amount": 49.99
  }
}

### Ingest batch
POST {{Ingestion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ingest/events/batch
Content-Type: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{CorrelationId}}

{
  "events": [
    {
      "eventType": "inventory.updated",
      "source": "warehouse-service",
      "payload": { "sku": "SKU-001", "quantity": 42 }
    },
    {
      "eventType": "inventory.updated",
      "source": "warehouse-service",
      "payload": { "sku": "SKU-002", "quantity": 7 }
    }
  ]
}

### Get event status
GET {{Ingestion.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ingest/events/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: {{CorrelationId}}
